dcterms:description: This dataset contains more than 10K conversations between two human users and has a rich set of diverse conversations spanning 55 user intents in the customer service domain. The key characteristic that makes this dataset relevant for our setting is that the agent is required to follow a set of agent guidelines, which makes the conversations inherently workflow-guided.

dcterms:description: This dataset contains more than 10k dialogues and is commonly used in task-oriented dialogue papers. Prior work has constructed workflows for this dataset, which we use as the ground truth workflows for training.
